1. Compute (Running code / servers)

These services help you run your application.

Amazon EC2
→ Rent virtual computers (servers) to run your app.
AWS Lambda
→ Run code without managing servers (auto runs when needed).
Amazon ECS
→ Run Docker containers easily.
Amazon EKS
→ Run Kubernetes (container management system).
AWS Elastic Beanstalk
→ Deploy app without worrying about infrastructure.
